name: UDefaultLevelSequenceInstanceData
doc: Default instance data class that level sequences understand. Implements IMovieSceneTransformOrigin.

TransformOriginActor: When set, this actor's world position will be used as the transform origin for all absolute transform sections
TransformOrigin: Specifies a transform that offsets all absolute transform sections in this sequence. Scale is ignored. Not applied to Relative or Additive sections.
